Bhim Singh醫院深切治療部。其同房病人本月15日確診染疫後，事主被轉入隔離病房作預防措施。由於隔離病房太熱，事主家屬當日買來冷風機，但在病房找不到插座，在未有徵詢醫護人員意見下自行拔除事主呼吸機的插蘇，改插了冷風機。<br />\n<br />\n事主呼吸機的電力近半小時後耗盡，家屬發現其情況轉差，急忙通知醫護進行心肺復蘇，惟事主終告不治。<br />\n<br />\n醫院表示，已成立3人調查委員會調查事件，委員會已取得隔離病房醫護的口供，但稱事主家屬沒有回應。院方又稱，事主去世後，其家屬對當值醫護「作出不當行為」。"},{"pid":"a6bec5392765094a403b499b7e80d3e340ee4ee5","tid":2073214,"uid":64710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"411c0064ba5c6e466f3bf598ce2abc27eddd0b17","tid":2073214,"uid":3204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ecc78defa1b31012a2b2c37ed4e693eba7bd00f","tid":2073214,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cdea1da9c0779d5618ab00c213242d38ea9350a","tid":2073214,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T06:58:32.000Z","msg":"蓋清水皮到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T07:15:00.000Z","msg":"咪講個水字啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T07:27:28.000Z","msg":"蓋清屎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T08:30:12.000Z","msg":"蓋清「深」潛"},{"pid":"42ed34f7e9d77bfe9899e36c31f0fba345bf5acf","tid":2073214,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T08:35:08.000Z","msg":"大家開多啲冷氣嚟對抗全球暖化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}